                  Decorative designs:
                  <locus target="#1r #27v" facs="003 030">folss. 1r, 27v, </locus> ornamental band;
                  <locus target="#iiv(erso) #62r" facs="003 064">iiv(erso), 62r, </locus> line of full stops;
                  <locus target="#27r #45v" facs="029 048">27r, 45v</locus> lines of alternating red and black dots
                  </decoNote>
